{"tid":1530952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九月開學先係主戰場！","createTime":"2019-09-02T05:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:55:15.000Z","uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad85c86755e30a30beae4427a50469297c5b5a35","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"今日罷工係明顯失敗<br />\n原因都無謂探究<br />\n跟本連sick leave都唔敢攞要等人塞鐵先被罷工既真係抵你做死一世奴隸<br />\n<br />\n但係睇返<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中學生罷課</span></strong>反而應該<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">升級</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跟本响學校做任何野都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">最低成本</span><br />\n學校本身就係一個聚人而資訊流通好快既地方<br />\n要<span style=\"color: gold;\">响assembly嗌口號 recess遊行 上堂present 派文宣</span>咩討論都得 行動又快<br />\n有咩事咪最多記大過囉<br />\n呢樣低b野跟本對升學就業係零影響<br />\n出得黎做野就知最叻最醒一定係反叛過 我身邊嗰班黎講出貓已經係最底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次出黎我都留意到好多中學生一睇就知係名校生<br />\n特別係女仔個頭梳到好整齊<br />\n名校有咩事都一定<span style=\"color: red;\">上報紙又有校友撐</span><br />\n最重要係呢班細路既學校有咩事<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">返送中龍頭勢力BK一定群起守護孩子</span><br />\n係人都知香港家長係勇武中的勇武<br />\n教書最驚你班家長<br />\n咁連登呢班支持一國一制既點夠打<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家幫手諗諗响學校仲有咩可以做<br />\n總之係要利用學校的環境再谷大個勢</span></span>"},{"pid":"27b3dfa71556b493721aa7de7458d00e7c7e9d11","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"742d94dc8c7a4424ca39bb5c3ecffee41d95d4cb","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c72d544d79b72da1a5a3f36169b527aff3eed17f","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"6c915d9fc69435d096d6e838fbdd99054936c212","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"b9b11cbfa6315ecacba5132882447445f8281806","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"721c309adac69c004d70a53d3d4b066083804745","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"620a275e092b4cdab79fc227fc105e3e8129f785","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7dd91e13896a157b4be2cdcbe7e189ebb63a40bc","tid":1530952,"uid":285619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"唉呀唔記得左p牌仔無得推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有等大家同意既幫忙推推"}]}